commit.message:
clang-format improvement,
automatical handling of attributes may decrease readability:
No good default, therefore using 'Leave'
Restore selection box size as prior to 62ac7b6

[luaAPI] Factor out getting elements from layer / selection

Reason: Reduce code duplication
Enable font hint metrics in PDF export
Add xopp, xopt, xoj file extensions to Info.plist
Use MIME type for export FileChooser filters
Replace some gtk3-only functions with gtk4 counterparts/wrappers
Switch locking logic in MissingPdfUndoAction to correspond to 914553f

Move document lock from UndoRedoHandler to UndoActions (#5365)

* Move UndoAction locks from UndoRedoHandler to UndoActions

- Removed document lock in UndoRedoHandler
- Added locks in all UndoActions to allow for more specific locking of function calls in UndoActions
- e.g. unlocking for fire...Changed function calls
